      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ds4tpkzth/image/upload/v1677676748/development/oc62t0alur9zba4q8a2y1lpwdqxd.jpg" alt="">
        <h4>Book a drone</h4>
        <p>Send an invits to the drone's owner!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/ds4tpkzth/image/upload/v1677667606/karl-greif-H5IXIH254AU-unsplash_ob9odk.jpg" alt="">
